    "client_msg_id": "5abc1469-b402-4b67-bb35-026e38b70568",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "I should write a large description, but dispatching actions instead of just events is wrong from my point of view, the UI just says what happened, not what should be done. Second, it's much easier just using something like immutable.js than reinventing structural sharing with weird js tricks. and last, it's a lot of boilerplate and those switch statements look like a code smell to me.",
